subject: Economy
question_en: What is the difference between public finance and private finance?
question_hi: सार्वजनिक व्यविद्यालय (Public Finance) aur कार्यक्रम (Private Finance) के औषध क्या हैं।
A_en: Public finance deals with government revenue, expenditure, and debt, while private finance focuses on individual and corporate finances.
